            <h4 class="h4">五.ISO13485认证</h4>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US">ISO13485</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">是一个独立的标准，对于仅在医疗产品工业领域经营的企业，该标准可以独立于</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US">ISO9001</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">使用。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">医疗器械行业过去一直使用</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US">ISO13485</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">标准（我国等同标准号为</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US">YY/T 0287</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">）作为质量管理体系认证的依据。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US">ISO13485</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">是一种质量认证体系，尤其是对医疗器械。在很多时候，医药公司在出口他们的产品到国际市场的时候，通过</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US">ISO9001/ISO13485</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">是占有优势的，甚至是必要的。在欧盟，欧盟的管理实现允许医疗器械的自由贸易。而符合欧盟管理的一个重要要求是质量体系的建立和独立评估。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">CE</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">认证是以建立</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">ISO13485</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">为基础的质量管理体系保证产品的安全、有效。</span><br />
            &nbsp;</td>
