            <h4 class="h4">六.FDA510K注册<font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'" lang="EN-US"><br />
            </span></font></h4>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">510(K)</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">文件也即<span lang="EN-US">FDA</span>对<span lang="EN-US">PMN</span>所需的文件，因其相应<span lang="EN-US">FD&amp;C Act</span>第<span lang="EN-US">510</span>章节，故通常称<span lang="EN-US">510</span>（<span lang="EN-US">K</span>）文件。对<span lang="EN-US">510</span>（<span lang="EN-US">K</span>）文件所必须包含的信息，其内容大致如下：<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">1.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">申请函；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">2.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">目录，即<span lang="EN-US">510</span>（<span lang="EN-US">K</span>）文件中所含全部资料的清单（包括附件）；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">3.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">真实性保证声明，对此声明，<span lang="EN-US">FDA</span>有一个标准的样本；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">4.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">器材名称，即产品通用名、<span lang="EN-US">FDA</span>分类名、产品贸易名；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">5.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">注册号码；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">6.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">分类；</font><span lang="EN-US"><br />
            </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">7.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">性能标准；</font><span lang="EN-US"><br />
            </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">8.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US"><font face="宋体"> </font></span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">产品标识；</font><span lang="EN-US"><br />
            </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;9.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">实质相等性比较（<span lang="EN-US">SE</span>）；</font><span lang="EN-US"><br />
            </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">10.</span><font face="宋体"><span style="font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">510</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt">（<span lang="EN-US">K</span>）摘要或声明；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>
            <p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; layout-grid-mode: char; mso-layout-grid-align: none"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">11.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">产品描述；</font><span lang="EN-US"><br />
            </span></span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt" lang="EN-US">12.</span><span style="font-size: 10.5pt"><font face="宋体">产品的安全性与有效性；<span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>
            <span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">13.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">生物相容性；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"><br />
