            &nbsp;15.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">软件验证（如适用）；</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US"><br />
            16.</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii&nbsp;-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA">灭菌（如适用）。</span><br />
